  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209960/extras/8e318399c42b46fb2a695795c45f16e0.avif?t=1743053164\" width=566 height=374 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209960/extras/82d0f07b762e167b2d323cb5a27cd7aa.avif?t=1743053164\" width=566 height=144 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I wake up in a familiar place. It feels like this is the first time I've opened my eyes.  <br>Something that everyone has, but I don't. They all call it a name. I didn't care about it much. <br>What I wonder about is who I have to find even though I don't know him at all.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                                           <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209960/extras/b49f093bcc6e84837ebee46d8f79a558.poster.avif?t=1743053164\" width=240 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209960/extras/b49f093bcc6e84837ebee46d8f79a558.webm?t=1743053164\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is the beginning of your adventure into mysterious lands. Met and separated from many characters to find a way to meet the man and discover the truth of this world.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209960/extras/9a13fdc50042bf733b52ce3f682a849c.poster.avif?t=1743053164\" width=566 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209960/extras/9a13fdc50042bf733b52ce3f682a849c.webm?t=1743053164\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209960/extras/fe3deb10720f2a60302bb768f5ea8718.avif?t=1743053164\" width=566 height=144 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >WiThu, It's Time To Go is an RPG Maker Horror game.<br>Most gameplay is dedicated to presenting the story and feelings of the situation. <br>You will have to go through many mini-games and puzzles. <br>Escape from danger. Talk and help who asking for. <br>Even though it may be our last time.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209960/extras/8e318399c42b46fb2a695795c45f16e0.avif?t=1743053164\" width=566 height=374 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209960/extras/82d0f07b762e167b2d323cb5a27cd7aa.avif?t=1743053164\" width=566 height=144 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I wake up in a familiar place. It feels like this is the first time I've opened my eyes.  <br>Something that everyone has, but I don't. They all call it a name. I didn't care about it much. <br>What I wonder about is who I have to find even though I don't know him at all.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                                           <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209960/extras/b49f093bcc6e84837ebee46d8f79a558.poster.avif?t=1743053164\" width=240 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209960/extras/b49f093bcc6e84837ebee46d8f79a558.webm?t=1743053164\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is the beginning of your adventure into mysterious lands. Met and separated from many characters to find a way to meet the man and discover the truth of this world.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209960/extras/9a13fdc50042bf733b52ce3f682a849c.poster.avif?t=1743053164\" width=566 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209960/extras/9a13fdc50042bf7